@NODE reco_PRU1 "* Format ProRunner v1.0 *"

 ******************************************************************
 * ------------ Heading model for << ProRunner 1.0 >> ----------- *
 * -------------------------------------------------------------- *
 * ---- Provenance : SILENTS "Something .....makes me sick" ----- *
 ******************************************************************

 As Wanton, this format is very similar to Protracker...
 Same heading till $438, where you must see "SNT."

 Then come the patterns packed like this :

      example  05 14 0C 04
                |  |  |  |
           sample  |  |  effect value
                   |  |
                note  effect (or commande)

 430: 00000000 00000000 534E542E 00000E01    ........SNT.....     
 440: 00000F05 05140C04 01010C00 05140C02    ................     
 450: 01010C00 00140C01 00000000 00140C01    ................     
 460: 00000000 00160C06 00000000 00160C03    ................     
 470: 00000000 00140C02 00000000 00140C02    ................     
@ENDNODE

