@NODE reco_Pygmy "* Format Pygmy Projects *"

******************************************************************
* ---------- Heading model for << Pygmy Projects >> ------------ *
* -------------------------------------------------------------- *
* ----- Provenance : "Extension" Demo from Pygmy Projects ------ *
